# repo-template Standard template for a GD repository.  #

**Please update this README with a name and description of your project.**

1./ SE will do the following manually
Create subnets with /26 mask bit (59 available IP) delegated to - "Microsoft.ContainerInstance/containerGroups" for each environment / location
Add subnets into allowed networks of the key vault (according to the environment / location)

az container create \
    --resource-group $ResourceGroup_ACI \
    --name $AzureContainerName \
    --image $imageName \
    --registry-username $ServicePrincipleAppId \
    --registry-password "$ServicePrinciplePassword" \
    --cpu $cpu \
    --memory $memory \
    --restart-policy $restartPolicy \
    --subnet $subnet \
    --environment-variables "ASPNETCORE_ENVIRONMENT=$envUpper" \
    --assign-identity
***********************************************************************************

2./SE create the resources via Terraform

Terraform azurerm-aci module: https://github.com/Green-Dot-Corporation/terraform-azurerm-aci
Reference composition repo: https://github.com/Green-Dot-Corporation/tf-az-aci-feedlistener-cbs
